------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------------------------------
BC03-MPAJHU STELLAR LIBRARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a library of select BC03 models used by the MPA-JHU catalog with
SDSS DR4 data.

The SSP templates have ages and metallicities as follows:

    Ages: 0.005, 0.025, 0.101, 0.286, 0.640, 0.904, 1.434, 2.500, 5.000,
          10.000 Gyr
       Z: 0.008, 0.004, 0.02, 0.05

The wavelengths were restricted to 3325 - 9295 just as a convenience to
keep the pixel sampling the same as the proviced data, 1 angstrom per
pixel.  We think the resolution is 2.3 angstroms, independent of
wavelength.

------------------------------------------------------------------------
------------------------------------------------------------------------
K.B. Westfall,  1 Mar 2018 - Provided by Christy Tremonti; 27 Feb 2018
